}}La '''Talia''' ([[talian]]: ''Italia'', {{IPA-it|iˈtaːlja||It-Italia.ogg}}), ufizielmënter la '''Republica Taliana'''<ref>{{cite web |title=United Nations – Change of name of country |url=http://unterm.un.org/dgaacs/unterm.nsf/c2f5f1ea9d52ce7485256dc5006e5940/a7c582eab561fa3f852573b600767fad/$FILE/Italy.pdf |website=unterm.un.org |publisher=United Nations |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304003523/http://unterm.un.org/dgaacs/unterm.nsf/c2f5f1ea9d52ce7485256dc5006e5940/a7c582eab561fa3f852573b600767fad/$FILE/Italy.pdf |archive-date=4 March 2016 |date=16 July 2003}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=OFFICIAL NAMES OF THE UNITED NATIONS MEMBERSHIP |url=https://www.un.int/protocol/sites/www.un.int/files/Protocol%20and%20Liaison%20Service/officialnamesofcountries.pdf |website=un.int |publisher=[[United Nations]] |access-date=18 February 2022}}</ref>([[talian]]: ''Repubblica Italiana'' {{IPA-it|reˈpubblika itaˈljaːna|}}) ie n paesc dl'[[Europa]] meridiunela y n cumëmber dl'[[Union europea|Union Europea]]. Posizioneda tl zënter dl [[Mer Mediterran]], iela ijuleda dal rest dl cuntinënt tres l massif dl'[[Elpes]].

L  cuntribut dla Talia ala zivilisazion uzidentela ie dastramb grand. La ie stata la cuna dl [[Empere roman]] y dla [[Renasciuda taliana]]. La Talia ie un di majeri atëures dla entraunides a livel internaziunel, cun si 60 milions de abitanc, fejela pert dla organisations internaziuneles plu imputrantes ([[NATO|Organisation dl Tratat de l Atlantich dl Nord]], [[Union europea|Union Europea]], [[G7|Grupa di Set]]).

